sentence: Among the underlying components of the Russell 3000 index, we saw noteworthy options trading volume today in Emerson Electric Co. (Symbol: EMR), where a total of 20,938 contracts have traded so far, representing approximately 2.1 million underlying shares.
That amounts to about 73.7% of EMR's average daily trading volume over the past month of 2.8 million shares.
Especially high volume was seen for the $68 strike call option expiring May 17, 2019, with 14,136 contracts trading so far today, representing approximately 1.4 million underlying shares of EMR.

Particularly high volume was seen for the $192.50 strike put option expiring May 10, 2019, with 1,205 contracts trading so far today, representing approximately 120,500 underlying shares of HD.
